        <Parent_String>Pahari (style) [300018997], Rajput (culture and style) [300019020], Indian painting styles [300018976], Indian (South Asian) [300018863], South Asian [300120222], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
